#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Roadheader and other mining vehicles"
msgstr "掘进机及其他采矿车辆"

#. ~ Description for Roadheader and other mining vehicles
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Adds a roadheader mining vehicle and its parts. Requires Tankmod: Revived."
msgstr "添加一台掘进机采矿车辆及其部件。需要 Tankmod: Revived。"

#: .\parts.json
msgid "roadheader"
msgid_plural "roadheaders"
msgstr[0] "掘进机"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'roadheader'}
#: .\parts.json
msgid ""
"A large and heavy jagged metalhead with a lot of spikes for destroying mine "
"walls."
msgstr "一个大型沉重的锯齿状金属头，带有许多尖刺，用于破坏矿墙。"

#: .\parts.json
msgid "Balancer"
msgid_plural "Balancers"
msgstr[0] "平衡器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Balancer'}
#: .\parts.json
msgid "A large and heavy metal bar for balancing a vehicle."
msgstr "一根大型沉重的金属棒，用于平衡车辆。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Balancer'}
#: .\parts.json
msgid "A large and heavy metal drum for balancing a vehicle."
msgstr "一个大型沉重的金属桶，用于平衡车辆。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'roadheader'}
#: .\parts.json
msgid ""
"A large metal jagged metalhead, powered by the vehicle's engines.  Use the "
"vehicle controls to turn it on or off.  When turned on, it will stop the "
"vehicle unless it has a strong engine.  When turned on, it will destroy "
"walls near it."
msgstr ""
"一个大型金属锯齿状金属头，由车辆引擎驱动。使用车辆控制装置开启或关闭。开启时，除非车辆有强劲引擎，否则会停止车辆。开启时，它会破坏附近的墙壁。"

#: .\vehicles.json
msgid "Roadheader"
msgstr "巷道掘进机"
